rompts/03-fastapi-scaffold.yolopilot.jsonlines:127:{\"color\": \"green\", \"emoji\": \"\\ud83d\\udcac\", \"event_type\": \"Agent Message\", \"message\": \"Implemented the FastAPI scaffold in commit `72e6065`. The backend now uses an app-factory layout with settings, services, models, DB placeholders, unversioned and versioned routers, `GET /health`, `GET /api/v1/health`, and a preserved `G...\", \"raw_event\": {\"item\": {\"id\": \"item_68\", \"text\": \"Implemented the FastAPI scaffold in commit `72e6065`. The backend now uses an app-factory layout with settings, services, models, DB placeholders, unversioned and versioned routers, `GET /health`, `GET /api/v1/health`, and a preserved `GET /api/hello` compatibility route. Key files are [main.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/app/main.py), [config.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/app/settings/config.py), [router.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/app/api/router.py), and [test_health.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/tests/test_health.py).\\n\\nVerification passed with backend pytest, `compileall`, live local startup plus `curl` checks, Docker Compose startup with the new `/health` healthcheck, and the existing browser smoke spec. The required reviewer summary was written last to [03-fastapi-scaffold.summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/prompts/03-fastapi-scaffold.summary.md). Current intentional limit: database wiring is still a scaffold and reports `not-configured` until later prompts.\", \"type\": \"agent_message\"}, \"type\": \"item.completed\"}, \"task_display_context\": {\"event_number\": 127, \"prompt_index\": 4, \"prompt_name\": \"03 \\u2014 Scaffold the FastAPI Backend\", \"prompt_total\": 100}, \"timestap\": \"2026-03-31T21:31:10-07:00\"}\nprompts/05-backend-settings-and-secrets-loading.yolopilot.jsonlines:1:{\"color\": \"blue\", \"emoji\": \"\\ud83e\\udd16\", \"event_type\": \"YoloPilot Event\", \"message\": \"Beginning task 6 of 100: 05-backend-settings-and-secrets-load