{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "Implemented a typed backend settings system with `secrets.yaml` support, readable validation failures, and Compose wiring that makes the repo-root secrets file available inside the backend container. The main work is in [config.py](/User...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_79", "text": "Implemented a typed backend settings system with `secrets.yaml` support, readable validation failures, and Compose wiring that makes the repo-root secrets file available inside the backend container. The main work is in [config.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/app/settings/config.py), with startup/error-path integration in [main.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/app/main.py) and [__main__.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/app/__main__.py), new docs in [secrets-and-local-config.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/docs/secrets-and-local-config.md), and a copyable example in [secrets.example.yaml](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/secrets.example.yaml). I also kept a legacy fallback for `STORYTELLER_GCS_BUCKET_NAME`, added typed feature flags, and updated health/status tests to match the new required-config model.\n\nVerification completed with `python -m pip install -r backend/requirements.txt`, `pytest backend/tests -q` (`11 passed`), a direct `create_app()` runtime check with valid env, a direct `python -m app` failure-path check showing concise no-traceback config errors, and `./scripts/dev-compose.sh config` for Compose validation. No browser or screenshot verification was needed because this task did not change UI behavior.\n\nCheckpoint commit: `1a4c598` with message `feat(prompt-05): backend settings and secrets loading`.\n\nRequired reviewer summary file written to [05-backend-settings-and-secrets-loading.summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/prompts/05-backend-settings-and-secrets-loading.summary.md).", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 151, "prompt_index": 6, "prompt_name": "05 \u2014 Backend Settings, Env Loading, and `secrets.yaml` Support", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-03-31T21:51:57-07:00"}
